ement\"><code>HTMLOptGroupElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLOptionElement\"><code>HTMLOptionElement</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLOptionsCollection\"><code>HTMLOptionsCollection</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLOutputElement\"><code>HTMLOutputElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLParagraphElement\"><code>HTMLParagraphElement</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLPictureElement\"><code>HTMLPictureElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLPreElement\"><code>HTMLPreElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLProgressElement\"><code>HTMLProgressElement</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLQuoteElement\"><code>HTMLQuoteElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLScriptElement\"><code>HTMLScriptElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLSelectElement\"><code>HTMLSelectElement</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLShadowElement\"><code>HTMLShadowElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLSourceElement\"><code>HTMLSourceElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLSpanElement\"><code>HTMLSpanElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLStyleElement\"><code>HTMLStyleElement</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableCaptionElement\"><code>HTMLTableCaptionElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableCellElement\"><code>HTMLTableCellElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableColElement\"><code>HTMLTableColElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableElement\"><code>HTMLTableElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableRowElement\"><code>HTMLTableRowElement</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableSectionElement\"><code>HTMLTableSectionElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLTemplateElement\"><code>HTMLTemplateElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLTextAreaElement\"><code>HTMLTextAreaElement</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTimeElement\"><code>HTMLTimeElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTitleElement\"><code>HTMLTitleElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTrackElement\"><code>HTMLTrackElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLUListElement\"><code>HTMLUListElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLUnknownElement\"><code>HTMLUnknownElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLVideoElement\"><code>HTMLVideoElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HashChangeEvent\"><code>HashChangeEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/History\"><code>History</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/ImageData\"><code>ImageData</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Location\"><code>Location</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MessageChannel\"><code>MessageChannel</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MessageEvent\"><code>MessageEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MessagePort\"><code>MessagePort</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Navigator\"><code>Navigator</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/PageTransitionEvent\"><code>PageTransitionEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Plugin\"><code>Plugin</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PluginArray\"><code>PluginArray</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PopStateEvent\"><code>PopStateEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/PromiseRejectionEvent\"><code>PromiseRejectionEvent</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RadioNodeList\"><code>RadioNodeList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/ValidityState\"><code>ValidityState</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"><div class=\"notecard deprecated\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>已废弃:</strong> 该特性已经从 Web 标准中删除，虽然一些浏览器目前仍然支持它，但也许会在未来的某个时间停止支持，请尽量不要使用该特性。</p></div></div>\n\n<p>The <strong><code>HTMLBaseFontElement</code></strong> interface provides special properties (beyond the regular <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a> interface it also has available to it by inheritance) for manipulating <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/CSS/CSS_Fonts_25d4b407d3e5044aeffb97faa9669a95\"><code>&lt;basefont&gt;</code></a> elements.</p>\n\n<p>The <code>&lt;basefont&gt;</code> element has been deprecated in HTML4 and removed in HTML5. This latest specification requires that this element implements <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLUnknownElement\"><code>HTMLUnknownElement</code></a> rather than <code>HTMLBaseFontElement</code>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>从父类 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a> 继承属性。</em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"htmlbasefontelement.color\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>HTMLBaseFontElement.color</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Is a <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a> representing the text color using either a named color or a color specified in the hexadecimal <code>#RRGGBB</code> format.</dd>\n <dt id=\"htmlbasefontelement.face\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>HTMLBaseFontElement.face</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Is a <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a> representing a list of one or more font names. The document text in the default style is rendered in the first font face that the client's browser supports. If no font listed is installed on the local system, the browser typically defaults to the proportional or fixed-width font for that system.</dd>\n <dt id=\"htmlbasefontelement.size\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>HTMLBaseFontElement.size</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Is a <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a> representing the font size as either a numeric or relative value. Numeric values range from <code>1</code> to <code>7</code> with <code>1</code> being the smallest and <code>3</code> the default. Relative value starts with a <code>'+'</code> or a <code>'-</code>'.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"方法","title":"方法","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>无具体方法；从父类 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a> 继承方法。</em></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"规范","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">规范</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状态</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">备注</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-HTML/html.html#ID-32774408\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Document Object Model (DOM) Level 2 HTML Specification<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">HTMLBaseFontElement</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-obsolete\">Obsolete</span></td>\n   <td>No change</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/REC-DOM-Level-1/level-one-html.html#ID-32774408\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Document Object Model (DOM) Level 1 Specification<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">HTMLBaseFontElement</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-obsolete\">Obsolete</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.HTMLBaseFontElement","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/CSS/CSS_Fonts/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect3\">\n\n\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>The HTML element <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/CSS/CSS_Fonts_25d4b407d3e5044aeffb97faa9669a95\"><code>&lt;basefont&gt;</code></a> <em>was</em> implementing this interface.</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"方法","id":"方法"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"The HTMLBaseFontElement interface provides special properties (beyond the regular HTMLElement interface it also has available to it by inheritance) for manipulating <basefont> elements.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"basefont","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<basefont>","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"HTMLBaseFontElement","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/conflicting/web/css/css_fonts","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/conflicting/web/css/css_fonts/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/CSS","title":"工具"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/CSS/CSS_Fonts","title":"HTMLBaseFontElement"}],"pageTitle":"HTMLBaseFontElement | MDN","noIndexing":true}}